name: Brainstorm
description:
Mental health is an issue that affects so many. This piece reflects mental health and how sensitive we are to the outside world.

The glass orb represents the brain, the gradient center orb is the creative soul. The clouds are the storm, the bad thoughts that come from time to time. They are always there, they can manifest in many ways, imposter syndrome, anxiety, worry, and stress.

Keep shining and weather that storm.
